ontrol of the buffer zone in Syria until an effective force enforces the 1974 Separation of Forces Agreement; supports Israeli official confirmation of control, while preserving the defensive/temporary framing.","sha256":"15b73465e3b7ba6773a7d5bf580e9b7e2a89780781c263fb74440cace16feb63","size_bytes":1134},{"phase":"arguments","role":"plaintiff","evidence_id":"ev_0d98a74d5144_submitted-evidence-03-plaintiff-0d98a74d5144","name":"submitted-evidence-03-plaintiff-0d98a74d5144.txt","title":"Israel PMO Mount Hermon statement, 17 Dec. 2024","source_url":"https://www.gov.il/en/pages/event-hermon171224","source_description":"Israel government Prime Minister's Office page identified by web search/open; direct local fetch returned HTTP 403, so this is a concise capture of visible indexed page text returned by web search on 2026-06-29.","mime_type":"text/plain","retrieval_timestamp":"2026-06-29T23:11:00Z","relevance":"Official Israeli statement placing Netanyahu at the summit of Mount Hermon on 17 Dec. 2024, receiving operational briefing, issuing directives on continued IDF deployment, and saying Israel would stay/deploy there until another arrangement ensures security.","sha256":"0d98a74d514423fb2dff49af0cc31ac1b604105eb75cb7b02dd7dd309b1864c8","size_bytes":2002},{"phase":"arguments","role":"plaintiff","evidence_id":"ev_63f356380079_submitted-evidence-04-plaintiff-63f356380079","name":"submitted-evidence-04-plaintiff-63f356380079.txt","title":"Jerusalem Post report: Israel takes over Syrian side of Mount Hermon, 8 Dec. 2024","source_url":"https://www.jpost.com/middle-east/article-832540","source_description":"Jerusalem Post article locally fetched and text-extracted 2026-06-29.","mime_type":"text/plain","retrieval_timestamp":"2026-06-29T23:11:30Z","relevance":"Credible contemporaneous reporting that on 8 Dec. 2024 the IDF took over the Syrian side of Mount Hermon to expand a demilitarized buffer zone, with IDF photo caption from the Syrian area of Mount Hermon.","sha256":"63f